Heat oil in heavy large skillet over medium-high heat. Add onion, garlic and Savory Market Golden Roast Chicken Flavor and saute until just tender, about 4 minutes. Add chicken and cook until chicken is brown, stirring constantly, about 3 minutes. Stir in vinegar, broth and mustard. Continue cooking until chicken is tender and cooked through, stirring constantly, about 3 minutes. Season with salt and pepper.